{"tid":1640620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[扯啱旗]究竟雙十應該扯咩旗","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:44:08.000Z","uid":257147,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a15d6cfef1cf3ffa21e29ec01c5ce0282658378","tid":1640620,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲都指出舉青天白日滿地紅嘅問題<br />\n而慶祝雙十嘅文宣依然用緊呢枝旗<br />\n<br />\n有無台灣巴絲可以了解下佢地對邊枝旗有共鳴？<br />\n然後文宣可以配合返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOAhuB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOAhuB8.png&h=37c3b0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQn0soO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQn0soO.jpg&h=0db37961&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0JGbQv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0JGbQv.jpg&h=f68efd23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c52a00ab5ac2fc64498803310c377fbddb8a147","tid":1640620,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/ROC_18Star.GIF?itok=zl2vVZQP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2FROC_18Star.GIF%3Fitok%3Dzl2vVZQP&h=58124f0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c7849202d774f980e6011f94ef096c6f611075e","tid":1640620,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"唔好扯d冇人識既旗"},{"pid":"b4a6c19444bfd23c1f542bd4f4f9963c597868f9","tid":1640620,"uid":75823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"第三面一定唔好，根本冇人識"},{"pid":"c744a7eb53165f6f6d2796c270f7eda3c5f3e9af","tid":1640620,"uid":235025,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2ec9461128c62116297045da48828a54c19824f","tid":1640620,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c52a00ab5ac2fc64498803310c377fbddb8a147","tid":1640620,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/ROC_18Star.GIF?itok=zl2vVZQP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2FROC_18Star.GIF%3Fitok%3Dzl2vVZQP&h=58124f0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"鐵血十八星 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceb9319c440d0f84b224ba32d1344059b79cec3","tid":1640620,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d964a5280c87713e465a559b1b2d87d1bf4a45fc","tid":1640620,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98cfff824bedb6559747a653d225ccd2e960f59e","tid":1640620,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"10月10號本身就係中華民國國慶，唔係台灣脫離中華民國獨立日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你雙十拎支台灣旗出黎唔通係想踩台灣當前政權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣未脫離中華民國，未廢中華民國國旗<br />\n中華民國係台灣目前最大公約數<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACfD1Fu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACfD1Fu.jpg&h=e6b8f0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ox6zz0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOx6zz0r.jpg&h=64d282cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更重要嘅係，香港人拎中華民國國旗落中共面，同台灣係冇必然關係嫁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人拎中華民國國旗=揮動美國、英國國旗=純粹落中共面</span></strong><br />\n我地&quot;今次&quot;唔係要為台灣主權帶風向話脫離埋中華民國明唔明呀<br />\n台灣成功脫離中華民國獨立，咁你先至係獨立日當日揮台灣旗啦，關雙十咩事呀"},{"pid":"0260d4c60ec519b2ae03b9167e66eb58b76bcd18","tid":1640620,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee546fc1420e046ab1b637dd7590ff511b8f86c0","tid":1640620,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M01TNFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM01TNFJ.jpg&h=76c9992b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以一齊舉？？無論藍綠都connect埋<br />\n張圖就係北洋五色旗同青天白日旗一齊"},{"pid":"724afdd1f2e70b83e0828957141e0912c4c223ac","tid":1640620,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0260d4c60ec519b2ae03b9167e66eb58b76bcd18","tid":1640620,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LksWLDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLksWLDf.png&h=b978385d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連深綠三立都未嫌棄，你會唔會過份解讀咗舉中華民國國旗嘅意義？<br />\n如果台灣主流已經去到脫離中華民國獨立，咁前一步會係嘗試修改中華民國憲法變成兩個中國先囉<br />\n<br />\n台灣正名公投連台南都只係五五開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />區區一班香港人仲想幫台灣正名？<br />\n同意票多於不同意票的行政區包括：臺南市（52.73%）、嘉義縣（51.59%）、屏東縣（50.46%）、宜蘭縣（50.41%）"},{"pid":"b6a7c275047e5dfafe513717dbbc7eb76d4236e2","tid":1640620,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:47:30.000Z","msg":"10月10 十十 雙十 公開祝賀盟幫<span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國</span>建國108年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640476</a>"},{"pid":"fc1e0b5abbaf89fa30a412a4e2d12a634e42777d","tid":1640620,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"紀念雙十，點少得十八星旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641102</a>"},{"pid":"7a76c6dd40b2cb574566dad4e4cb1b1267e6457d","tid":1640620,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"如果舉青天白日，係旨在激鳩中共而並非以connect 台灣為前提<br />\n<br />\n同樣情況，如果 NBA 入場嘅人要扯旗<br />\n作為香港人，你會想佢地舉一面點樣嘅旗？<br />\n單純地一面紅底抽氣扇？<br />\n定黑底？港英？龍獅？<br />\n定係黑底白字光復香港時代革命？"},{"pid":"c0f946fd82fb79f25d55db750798d3ae1e95e23b","tid":1640620,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"724afdd1f2e70b83e0828957141e0912c4c223ac","tid":1640620,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0260d4c60ec519b2ae03b9167e66eb58b76bcd18","tid":1640620,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LksWLDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLksWLDf.png&h=b978385d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連深綠三立都未嫌棄，你會唔會過份解讀咗舉中華民國國旗嘅意義？<br />\n如果台灣主流已經去到脫離中華民國獨立，咁前一步會係嘗試修改中華民國憲法變成兩個中國先囉<br />\n<br />\n台灣正名公投連台南都只係五五開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />區區一班香港人仲想幫台灣正名？<br />\n同意票多於不同意票的行政區包括：臺南市（52.73%）、嘉義縣（51.59%）、屏東縣（50.46%）、宜蘭縣（50.41%）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"我無嘗試解讀，亦都無preference <br />\n<br />\n只不過有好幾個post 指出青天白日帶來嘅問題<br />\n開放畀大家討論吓咁解"},{"pid":"81630db259307701af6868fec398ab235798c6fb","tid":1640620,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a76c6dd40b2cb574566dad4e4cb1b1267e6457d","tid":1640620,"